pos_examples: Now, cut board teddy into part frame_9 using highspeed-saw star_213 with awood kumquat, surface roof_11, changing size from aboardsize rain to aboardsize rain_94 through intermediate sizes aboardsize rain_94_21 and aboardsize rain_31.
(cut-board-large teddy frame_9 star_213 kumquat roof_11 rain rain_31 rain_94_21 rain_94)

Once you are done, please saw board teddy into medium part frame_9 using saw screen with awood kumquat, surface roof_11, changing size from aboardsize rain to aboardsize rain_94 through intermediate size aboardsize rain_31.
(do-saw-medium teddy frame_9 screen kumquat roof_11 rain rain_31 rain_94)
First, load board teddy into highspeed-saw star_213 and then do spray varnish on part frame_9 using spray-varnisher object_50 to change color to acolour bastion with surface roof_11.

(load-highspeed-saw teddy star_213)
(do-spray-varnish frame_9 object_50 bastion roof_11)

The next step is to do grind on part frame_9 using grinder kumquat_8 to change surface from surface roof_11 to verysmooth, color from acolour bastion to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus object_260 to treatmentstatus object_260_76.
(do-grind frame_9 kumquat_8 roof_11 bastion object_260 object_260_76)
